00:00:24.046 --> 00:00:26.640
is called "10 Red Hot Tips
to Promotoe Your Business."

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:30.400
Basically, it's geared to people
in the small-to-medium-size

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:31.370
enterprises.

00:00:31.370 --> 00:00:34.030
And it's really teaching them
