00:44:59.620 --> 00:45:01.320
in a very initial phase.

00:45:01.320 --> 00:45:04.640
So, do you have an example of--

00:45:04.640 --> 00:45:07.150
good example of
how some business

00:45:07.150 --> 00:45:12.147
could have recovered from
a bad usage of sponsorship?

00:45:12.147 --> 00:45:13.730
ELLEN GUNNING: It's
a very interesting

00:45:13.730 --> 00:45:14.813
[INAUDIBLE] on reputation.

00:45:14.813 --> 00:45:16.640
Reputation takes a
lifetime to build,

00:45:16.640 --> 00:45:18.570
and about 30 seconds to lose.

00:45:18.570 --> 00:45:20.950
Was it Warren Buffett
who said, if you

00:45:20.950 --> 00:45:23.912
think that everything you
do will be publicly known,

00:45:23.912 --> 00:45:25.620
you'll be very careful
about what you do.

00:45:25.620 --> 00:45:28.630
And that's about reputation,
because you lose reputation

00:45:28.630 --> 00:45:29.320
very easily.

00:45:29.320 --> 00:45:31.760
People do very stupid
things with reputation.

00:45:31.760 --> 00:45:36.090
Probably one of the
best examples was the--

00:45:36.090 --> 00:45:37.590
I can't get the
name of the company.

00:45:37.590 --> 00:45:39.410
Was it [? Tremmell? ?]
The company

00:45:39.410 --> 00:45:41.740
who had-- do you remember
when there was-- going back

00:45:41.740 --> 00:45:45.130
25 years or more, the company
where that guy was actually

00:45:45.130 --> 00:45:48.268
injecting Tylenol into
tablets in the States?

00:45:48.268 --> 00:45:50.616
And it was Tylenol tablets.

00:45:50.616 --> 00:45:51.990
I just remembered
the brand name.

00:45:51.990 --> 00:45:54.870
They used injecting cyanide
into Tylenol tablets.

00:45:54.870 --> 00:45:57.520
Anyway, it made people
very nervous about actually

00:45:57.520 --> 00:45:58.360
using the product.

00:45:58.360 --> 00:45:59.530
And they had a great reputation.

00:45:59.530 --> 00:46:00.450
They were very well known.

00:46:00.450 --> 00:46:02.560
And what they did was--
and most people in New York

00:46:02.560 --> 00:46:03.820
thought they were
crazy at the time.

00:46:03.820 --> 00:46:05.945
What they did was they
withdrew all of the products

00:46:05.945 --> 00:46:06.654
from the shelves.

00:46:06.654 --> 00:46:08.445
And they put messages
up everywhere saying,

00:46:08.445 --> 00:46:09.520
do not use our product.

00:46:09.520 --> 00:46:10.820
If you have it at
home, bring it back.

00:46:10.820 --> 00:46:11.700
We'll give you a full refund.

00:46:11.700 --> 00:46:13.350
For God's sake, don't
take any tablets.

00:46:13.350 --> 00:46:14.600
We don't know what's going on.

00:46:14.600 --> 00:46:16.640
We don't want anybody to
die because they've taken--

00:46:16.640 --> 00:46:18.390
I think two people
in New York had died.

00:46:18.390 --> 00:46:20.380
And we don't know
what's happened.

00:46:20.380 --> 00:46:22.235
Everybody said, you
know, great move.

00:46:22.235 --> 00:46:24.860
From PR point of view, obviously
they care about the customers.

00:46:24.860 --> 00:46:27.170
They're going to have
nothing left to come back to,

00:46:27.170 --> 00:46:28.520
because they've left this
gap, and their competitors

00:46:28.520 --> 00:46:29.590
were taking over.

00:46:29.590 --> 00:46:33.377
And when they came back, they
came back with that foil seal.

00:46:33.377 --> 00:46:35.335
And they said, so now
we've made it extra safe.

00:46:35.335 --> 00:46:36.740
So now you will
know if anybody has

00:46:36.740 --> 00:46:37.906
tampered with these tablets.

00:46:37.906 --> 00:46:38.500
You'd check.

00:46:38.500 --> 00:46:39.320
Seals shouldn't be broken.

00:46:39.320 --> 00:46:40.340
The foil should be intact.

00:46:40.340 --> 00:46:42.474
It was very clever, and
they recovered market share

00:46:42.474 --> 00:46:44.580
very quickly because
people actually said,

00:46:44.580 --> 00:46:46.630
they care about us.

00:46:46.630 --> 00:46:48.390
An example of one
who got it very wrong

00:46:48.390 --> 00:46:51.505
was Shell in the States, when
they did all that damage.

00:46:51.505 --> 00:46:53.590
And they sent over-- and
where they got it wrong

00:46:53.590 --> 00:46:54.773
was from minute one.

00:46:54.773 --> 00:46:58.490
They sent over an English
chief executive, an English PR

00:46:58.490 --> 00:46:59.490
person--

00:46:59.490 --> 00:47:01.430
or UK PR person,
and a UK lawyer.

00:47:01.430 --> 00:47:03.596
So you had-- you're in the
States, (AMERICAN ACCENT)

00:47:03.596 --> 00:47:04.570
where talks like this, OK?

00:47:04.570 --> 00:47:05.510
So like, what to they do?

00:47:05.510 --> 00:47:07.440
OK, they're after messing
the whole thing up,

00:47:07.440 --> 00:47:09.513
and you get, (BRITISH ACCENT)
hello, I'm a chief executive.

00:47:09.513 --> 00:47:10.870
And I'm over here, an American.

00:47:10.870 --> 00:47:11.912
I'm going to sort it out.

00:47:11.912 --> 00:47:12.953
Hello, I'm the PR person.

00:47:12.953 --> 00:47:13.960
I'm over here with him.

00:47:13.960 --> 00:47:17.090
Just common sense says respect
the country that you're in.

00:47:17.090 --> 00:47:18.800
Now, that's down to reputation.

00:47:18.800 --> 00:47:21.480
If you actually respect your
customers, like once you get

00:47:21.480 --> 00:47:24.440
somebody with local eyes
and ears on the ground,

00:47:24.440 --> 00:47:28.250
you get somebody who's American
who says this is how it works.

00:47:28.250 --> 00:47:29.440
This is how-- just language.

00:47:29.440 --> 00:47:32.035
This is how people will
interpret what you're saying.

00:47:32.035 --> 00:47:33.929
And their reputation
suffered massively.

00:47:33.929 --> 00:47:35.470
I'm not sure that
it's recovered yet.

00:47:35.470 --> 00:47:38.442
But you'll find enough
of that company,

00:47:38.442 --> 00:47:40.150
when their reputation's
severely damaged,

00:47:40.150 --> 00:47:43.010
they actually completely
rename the company,

00:47:43.010 --> 00:47:44.899
because they didn't--
the research says you

00:47:44.899 --> 00:47:47.190
won't recover, as people will
always associate you with

00:47:47.190 --> 00:47:48.670
the disaster.

00:47:48.670 --> 00:47:50.850
So they have no option.

00:47:50.850 --> 00:47:53.696
But it's a good example
of if you don't get right,

00:47:53.696 --> 00:47:54.820
how much damage you can do.

00:47:54.820 --> 00:47:56.027
That's the other side.

